Empath::

The 'Lady' catches up with the duo.  "Honestly, Windlord, quit 
worrying about me."  Empath rolls her eyes, a bit disconcerting since 
she's in beast mode.  "I'm a Predacon, remember?  Why do I merit such 
special treatment?"

--- In nbwrpg@y..., Rudra656@a... wrote:
> ::Aerotaur::
>        He looks up from where he was watching the Predacons 
leave.  "Yes, 
> Windlord, I am fine."  He turns and walks over to him.  "Although 
it appears 
> you are not."  He shrugs and gestures to the Predacons.  "But at 
least we 
> have won the day."
